variables.title: X_d
variables.variableValue:
PU_AVG(DOMAIN_TABLE(LFA1.NAME1),(
    CASE
        -- no reqeusted due date (not part of the analysis)
        WHEN ISNULL("EKET"."EINDT") = 1 THEN NULL 
        -- requested due date in the future 
        WHEN ISNULL(PU_LAST(EKPO,"_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME","_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN"='Record Goods Receipt')) = 1 AND DAYS_BETWEEN(TODAY()  ,"EKET"."EINDT") >= 0 THEN NULL 
        -- no goods receipt and requested due date more than the tolerance in the past, seen as 'overdue' 
        WHEN ISNULL(PU_LAST(EKPO,"_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME","_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN"='Record Goods Receipt')) = 1 AND DAYS_BETWEEN(TODAY()  ,"EKET"."EINDT") < (-1.0 * 5) THEN 0.0 
        -- no goods receipt and requested due date in the past, but still in the tolerance buffer
        WHEN ISNULL(PU_LAST(EKPO,"_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME","_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN"='Record Goods Receipt')) = 1 AND DAYS_BETWEEN(TODAY()  ,"EKET"."EINDT") >= (-1.0 * 5) THEN NULL
        -- delivery during the tolerance buffer
        WHEN PU_COUNT("EKPO", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Record Goods Receipt' ) > 0
        AND DAYS_BETWEEN("EKET"."EINDT", PU_LAST(EKPO,"_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME","_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN"='Record Goods Receipt')) <= 5
        AND  DAYS_BETWEEN("EKET"."EINDT", PU_LAST(EKPO,"_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME","_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN"='Record Goods Receipt')) >= (-1.0 * 10)
        THEN 1.0 
        -- else: delivery too early or too late
        ELSE 0.0 
    END
) *100)
